  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dd6\u0db4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dbd\u0db6\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db4\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dba\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who infiltrated the television and disturbed the country was caught while trying to jump",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior police officer said that one of the two people who entered the Sri Lanka Television Corporation and joined its live broadcast claiming to be activists was arrested this afternoon (26) when he was about to leave Katunayake International Airport for Dubai.",
        "It is reported that while he was sitting on the plane belonging to Sri Lankan Airlines, a group of about four officers of the Criminal Investigation Department (CID) entered the plane and forcibly took him out of the plane and said that there was a court warrant for his arrest.",
        "However, an immigration and emigration officer at Katunayake Airport said in a query tonight that the immigration and emigration department had not received a court warrant for the arrested person and that he was arrested while taking his seat on the plane after completing the immigration and emigration procedures.",
        "It is reported that at the time of his arrest, the police officers did not present a warrant obtained from the court and many passengers including foreigners on the plane protested.",
        "It is further learned that there was a heated situation in the plane due to his fight with the police officers.",
        "It is also reported that a group of people claiming to be militants staged a protest near the main entrance of the Sri Lanka Television Corporation on the 13th and Dhanish Ali and another person entered the television corporation and joined its live broadcast."
      ],
